# 📈 SB Stocks

SB Stocks is a user-friendly paper trading web application designed for stock market enthusiasts who want to practice and improve their trading skills without any financial risk.

The platform provides real-time US stock market data, historical trends, and virtual portfolio management, allowing users to simulate trading in a realistic environment. Whether you're a beginner learning the basics or an experienced trader testing new strategies, SB Stocks offers a secure, intuitive, and educational experience.

---

